==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sparry
<hw>Spar"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Spar</er>.]</ety> <def>Resembling spar, or consisting of spar;
abounding with spar; having a confused crystalline structure;
spathose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Sparry iron</b></col> <fld>(Min.)</fld>, <cd>siderite.
See <er>Siderite</er> <sd>(a)</sd>.</cd> -- <col><b>Sparry
limestone</b></col> <fld>(Min.)</fld>, <cd>a coarsely crystalline
marble.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sparse</ent>⟦br⟧
